cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper discusses intelligent user interfaces for efficient information capture, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The specific interfaces discussed, such as handwriting recognition and predictive fillin, involve natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents quantitative results, which could be considered a form of information retrieval (cs.IR) and data analysis (cs.LG).
